        {
            "title": "英超│熱刺0:2阿士東維拉 全副選出戰徹底擺爛 為歐霸決賽去到盡",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"熱刺全副選出戰徹底擺爛，0:2不敵維拉。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4e92444b2004c45295dad3b344962613/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051704314997396.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">熱刺全副選出戰徹底擺爛，0:2不敵維拉。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>熱刺在周五英超作客阿士東維拉利時，正選陣容除剛傷瘉要尋找狀態的隊長孫興民外，其餘全部都是副選，為留力下周三歐霸決賽去到盡。這支倫敦球會最終因為徹底擺爛，以0:2不敵維拉，全失3分。\n\n</p><h2>正選僅孫興民一名主力</h2>\n<p>今場熱刺的正選陣容，基本上全部都是副選，包括門將堅斯基、中堅奇雲丹素、中場艾捷格雷、翼鋒米基摩亞等，只有因為剛傷瘉需要尋找比賽狀態的孫興民，是11人中唯一的主力。他們因為人腳不整而大部份時間受壓，僅靠孫興民策動快速反擊取得零星的攻勢，幸好半場賽和0:0。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺今場的正選陣容，大部份都是副選。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6d38ecd29ea3afdede50caac04246c25/2025-05/1_46.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺今場的正選陣容，大部份都是副選。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"門將用上副選堅斯基。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/49fd53d8b34f5a3446cb191f2f6c9e54/2025-05/2_36.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        門將用上副選堅斯基。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"右閘是後備的史賓斯。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/462e519b9c096580cd0d96a758b8c0a8/2025-05/3_44.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        右閘是後備的史賓斯。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"孫興民是唯一踢正選的熱刺主將。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e4c1688c086c9775192f0dd5918f087/2025-05/4_38.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        孫興民是唯一踢正選的熱刺主將。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"孫興民策動反擊。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ac507efbcbd62bc44950f8c1d705ba12/2025-05/5_35.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        孫興民策動反擊。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺領隊普斯迪高古為了歐霸決賽去到盡。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0c6390331e1c05299c502f1ac271779/2025-05/6_17.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺領隊普斯迪高古為了歐霸決賽去到盡。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>安斯干沙開紀錄</h2>\n<p>然而他們守到59分鐘終於失守，維拉前鋒奧尼屈堅斯在一次角球攻勢中頭槌二傳，中堅安斯干沙近門抽射入網打破僵局。主隊之後繼續控制戰局，中場保巴卡卡馬拉於73分鐘接應鋒將摩根羅渣士的妙傳，射成2:0，維拉最終亦以這比數奏捷。而熱刺將聯賽不勝走勢增至6場，賽後繼續排第17位。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安斯干沙為維拉攻入第一球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/421c1c6382c7c97b3b33949565996ee3/2025-05/7_26.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安斯干沙為維拉攻入第一球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安斯干沙近門射入。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e31e6a9f40c7085a047eccd5e30c7907/2025-05/8_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安斯干沙近門射入。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安斯干沙慶祝取得入球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/136a955c5512f90d4741ef594557d86b/2025-05/9_13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安斯干沙慶祝取得入球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保巴卡卡馬拉射入2:0。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee1999a3c7e3f4cbcfe5f4a963d28782/2025-05/10_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保巴卡卡馬拉射入2:0。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保巴卡卡馬拉射入2:0。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d162bc90c758bdf4be46965351e73867/2025-05/11_9.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保巴卡卡馬拉射入2:0。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
