            "title": "13歲男童荃灣大河道突跑出馬路 捱貨車撞頭部流血送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Facebook 車cam L群組\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c273674fe5bb7de41f31546a5ca7870e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051704052845564.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Facebook 車cam L群組</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荃灣發生交通意外。昨日（16日）傍晚6時許，一輛中型貨車沿大河道往沙咀道方向行駛時，一名13歲男童突然從車頭由右至左跑出馬路，貨車收掣不及，男童捱撞倒地，頭部流血，四肢擦傷，幸保持清醒。\n\n</p>\n<p>救援人員接報到場，即場為男童作簡單料理，然後送瑪嘉烈醫院作進一步治理。從網上圖片見到，男童倒臥在馬路上，多名救護員為他檢查傷勢，現場馬路一度被封，大批乘客在巴士站候車。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253393/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"從網上圖片見到，男童倒臥在馬路上，多名救護員現場為他檢查傷勢。Facebook 車cam L群組\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c733f5327a5056b2badbd9af3938833/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_8_34_41_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        從網上圖片見到，男童倒臥在馬路上，多名救護員現場為他檢查傷勢。Facebook 車cam L群組\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253394/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"從網上圖片見到，男童倒臥在馬路上，多名救護員現場為他檢查傷勢。Facebook 車cam L群組\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3bfbc61c5e30ed26bea797675a11b399/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_8_34_54_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        從網上圖片見到，男童倒臥在馬路上，多名救護員現場為他檢查傷勢。Facebook 車cam L群組\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
