            "title": "一家四口旅遊歸來驚見陌生漢霸屋 寓所變亂葬崗家財盡失 只是噩夢開始",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"10 News 畫面截圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/35f417a6d1e826d32a444d5f3522c847/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051702234221539.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">10 News 畫面截圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>澳洲維多利亞州一個家庭近日遭遇駭人經歷，一家四口從尼泊爾探親旅遊返國後，竟發現所租住的住所被不明人士非法佔據，髒亂如亂葬崗，而且屋內物品被洗劫一空，連孩子的用品及祖傳金飾亦不翼而飛，損失超過5萬澳元（約25萬港元）。\n\n</p>\n<p>事主是居於謝珀頓（<b>Shepparton</b>）的初級醫生奎克（<b>Sanjay Kuikel</b>），與太太高塔姆（Nilima Gautam）及兩名分別3歲與1歲大的子女於五月3日結束為期三周的探親行程返抵澳洲，未料甫打開門便見一名男子坐在他們的沙發上，邊看電視、邊抽煙、邊吃披薩，彷彿自己是屋主。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253285/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/48a7e199a1076abb1b6bf88b5a5b2c86/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_32_31_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253286/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3fbace0b28c53f5bf77fd86054e47d9/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_27_51_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253287/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd0f74f63fba39cc883b040c43facfa1/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_31_39_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253288/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6331e0e31b5de695d490601ee585eca/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_31_59_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253289/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a2f4eeb1a933a7608815f84b3a323da8/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_32_07_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253290/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d06b4f1b224614bef30868b85bf2c6e5/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_32_13_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253291/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d9910130bdc0c52fd5306432b4e953a0/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_33_12_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253292/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee801318f2c51f7f2f91e926c8ff56e9/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_32_49_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253293/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4fb5cb10c7d4df37e935d7e28c987e6b/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_31_27_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>「我丈夫問他：『你是誰？』他居然回答：『我住這裡。』」高塔姆接受當地傳媒《10 News》訪問時回憶道，她們當時十分震驚和恐懼，尤其身旁還有孩子，「他們可能有武器，真的很可怕」。\n\n</p>\n<p>高塔姆一家馬上報警，警方隨後將男子帶走，然而，這只是這家人噩夢的開始。之後，該名陌生男多次返回住所，堅稱房屋「已經是他的」。最離諎的是，高塔姆和丈夫把門鎖更換防止再人擅闖，但其後竟發現門鎖被人破壞並被換上另一把新門鎖，那名陌生男多次擅自闖入，甚至將毒品器具、酒精、日用品、雜貨一併搬入屋內，視若無人，令高塔姆一家既無奈又懼怕。\n\n</p>\n<p>高塔姆透露，警方曾告知她，當她們一家外出旅遊期間，有多達<b>17</b>至<b>20</b>人每日出入她的家，喧嘩玩樂，令鄰居不勝其擾，更因噪音與醉酒滋擾問題多次報警。\n\n</p>\n<p>而高塔姆視察屋內環境後更幾乎暈倒，因為本來潔淨整齊的住所已亂如亂葬崗，幾乎所有衣服被翻出並被撕爛，物件隨處亂放，客廳、廚房裡到處放了酒和大麻，\n\n</p>\n<p>屋內物品亦被洗劫一空，損失包括金銀首飾、婚嫁禮物、衣物、廚具及小孩用品，連高塔姆亡父贈送的結婚金飾也遭盜走，令她心痛不已。\n\n</p>\n<p>當地警方表示，由於男子多次返回受害者家中，並且違反禁制令，目前已經將他逮捕及起訴，案件正在調查中。\n\n</p>\n<p>為怕陌生人再次折返鬧事，高塔姆全家一度被迫搬入臨時住宿地點。高塔姆和丈夫在募款平台<b>GoFundMe</b>發起籌款，目標籌集一萬澳元（約5萬港元），以補貼生活必需品、短期住宿開支，並為孩子提供穩定環境。他寫道：「這次經歷摧毀了我們的安全感與心靈平靜，我一生致力於照顧他人，如今我和家人急需援助。」\n\n</p>\n<p>截至目前，籌款已達4,000澳元。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069341/即時-國際-一家四口旅遊歸來驚見陌生漢霸屋-寓所變亂葬崗家財盡失-只是噩夢開始",
