            "title": "東涌的士私家車相撞釀3傷 掃毀4米欄零件四散",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"facebook圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/eeccfb3930ee463967ff17b02eaad9a5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051701180715120.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">facebook圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（17日）凌晨零時許，東涌發生車禍，一輛俗稱「小露寶」的混能的士和另一輛私家車在裕東路和順東路交界相撞，2男1女受輕傷，清醒送院治理。\n\n</p>\n<p>網上圖片可見，車禍後，的士撞向路中草叢圍欄，車門打開；私家車橫亘路中，車頭損毀嚴重。兩車零件四散，滿佈馬路。現場有4米欄杆被掃毀，裕東路往九龍方向兩條行車線一度封閉。警方到場調查車禍成因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253270/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車橫亘路中，車頭損毀嚴重。Facebook圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e2025bcd449fbf9b22b9bd1f07e9d3a/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_01_49_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車橫亘路中，車頭損毀嚴重。Facebook圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253271/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"車禍後，的士撞向路中草叢圍欄，車門打開。Facebook圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bf605d0a3df4f64f0a298305609b160e/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-16_at_6_14_03_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車禍後，的士撞向路中草叢圍欄，車門打開。Facebook圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
